source("theme_mine.R")
source("functions.R")

# load library
library(tidyverse)
library(ggthemes)
library(scales)
library(ggrastr)
library(vegan)
library(data.table)
tidy_col <- c("#18BC9C","#CCBE93","#a6cee3","#1f78b4","#b2df8a","#fb9a99","#fdbf6f","#ff7f00","#cab2d6","#6a3d9a")
pal <- tableau_color_pal("Superfishel Stone")
col <- pal(10)

Evaluate the robustness of the model

d1 <- read_rds("out/rds/external_validation.GALAXY.mOTUs.rds")
d2 <- read_rds("out/rds/external_validation.MetaCardis.mOTUs.rds")

md1 <- fread("data/GALAXY_load.tsv")
md2 <- fread("data/MetaCardis_load.tsv")

d2$cohort <- md1$cohort
d1$cohort <- md2$cohort

## GALAXY/MicrobLiver
p1 <- ggplot(d2, aes(x = count, y = pred)) +
  theme_mine() +
  geom_abline(linetype = 2, col = "gray") +  
  geom_point_rast(stroke = 0, col = col[4], size = 0.8, alpha = 0.8) +
  ggpubr::stat_cor(size = 3) +
  geom_smooth(method = "lm") +
  xlab("Microbial load") +
  ylab("Predicted value") +
  ggtitle("GALAXY/MicrobLiver") +
  facet_wrap(~cohort, ncol = 6)
p1
## `geom_smooth()` using formula = 'y ~ x'

## MetaCardis
p2 <- ggplot(d1, aes(x = count, y = pred)) +
  theme_mine() +
  geom_abline(linetype = 2, col = "gray") +  
  geom_point_rast(stroke = 0, col = col[6], size = 0.8, alpha = 0.8) +
  ggpubr::stat_cor(size = 3) +
  geom_smooth(method = "lm") +
  xlab("Microbial load") +
  ylab("Predicted value") +
  ggtitle("MetaCardis") +
  facet_wrap(~cohort, ncol = 6)
p2

Evaluate effects of technical variability

df <- read_rds("out/rds/df.technical_variability.rds")
pair <- combn(levels(df$group), 2, simplify = F)

p.box <- ggplot(df, aes(x = group, y = abs(pred_diff2), fill = group)) +
  theme_mine() +
  geom_violin() +
  geom_hline(yintercept = 0, linetype = 2) +
  geom_boxplot(width = 0.2, outlier.size = 0.1, fill = "white") +
  ggpubr::stat_compare_means(comparisons = pair, method = "wilcox.test", tip.length = NA, label = "p.signif") +
  theme(axis.title.x = element_blank()) +
  ylab("Absolute log2 fold change\nin microbial load") +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1)) +
  theme(legend.position = "none") +
  scale_x_discrete(labels = c("Within sample\n(same protocols, different labs)", "Within sample\n(different DNA ext.)", "Within individual\n(time-series sample)", "Between individuals")) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = tidy_col[3:6])
p.box
